name: Is it his birthday yet?
description: Is it his birthday yet, when he walks out of the room? He's dying to be born, he is learning to be a man, but just how long is long in a man? How many kisses does it take before his face turns red? Hips like shards, veins like chiselled lead, this handsome boy wants nothing more than to be left alone. But Raggedy Annabel is his constant companion, his constant companion from infancy to old age, and when the time comes for him to walks out of the room, he'll cling to Raggedy Annabel like a sonnet.
